title: Contributor element schema
description: Contributor element schema generated by the CEDAR Template Editor 2.5.38

propertyDescriptions.contributorRole: The role of the contributor in bringing the described dataset into existence.
propertyDescriptions.contributorType: The type of the contributor of the described dataset (organization, person, or system).
propertyDescriptions.contributorEmail: An email address of the contributor.

propertyDescriptions.contributorName: The full name of the contributor.
propertyDescriptions.contributorGivenName: If the contributor is a person, the personal name(s) of the contributor (e.g., first and optionally middle name in Western languagues, optionally middle and last name in Asian languages).
propertyDescriptions.contributorFamilyName: If the contributor is a person, the surname(s) of the contributor (e.g., last name in Western languagues, first name in Asian languages).
